<HEAD>

<TITLE>Power to the parents? The story of education vouchers, by Cohen & Farrar, Summer, 1977, The Public Interest</TITLE>

</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#800080" ALINK="#8000FF"><center><IMG SRC="http://www.schoolreport.com/epi/gifs/epianim.gif" WIDTH=40% align=bottom alt="Education Policy Institute"></center>
