<P>The figures in Table 1.1 overestimate the membership and underestimate the revenues of the merged organization; since the revenues will be discussed in more detail in Chapter 3, we will comment here only on the membership figures.</P>
<P>From its <I>Strategic Plan and Budget, Fiscal Year 1993-94</I>, the total NEA 1993-94 membership figures includes the following:</P>
