<P>The district has also hired nine employees to work in its communications department.  In 1993, DISD hired a compensation specialist to review salary ranges of employees.  </P>
<H4><B>Arizona group receives newspaper award </B></H4>
<P>The Arizona School Choice Trust is a privately funded scholarship plan which operates much like the Dallas CEF.  The charitable organization will receive the Washington Times National Service Award for their efforts in providing educational opportunities to low-income children.  The award is presented annually to groups and individuals who promote the integrity of the family, support youth and contribute to society.  One of the largest benefactors of the Arizona School Choice Trust is the Phoenix Suns.  </P>
