  <head>
    <title><B>Sweet success.</B> How I beat the union.</title>
  </head>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../../gifs/wcnback.gif" BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004000" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#804000" ALINK="#FF8000">
