Germany, Hungary)</em></strong></td>
<td valign="top"><strong>63.0</strong></td>
<td valign="top"><strong>526.6</strong></td>
<td valign="top"><strong>69.2</strong></td></tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"></strong>
<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2"><strong>Countries with 60 % or less
union membership rate</td>
<td valign="top"></td>
