<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">
<p>The cost of this agenda can be put in perspective by comparing it to the costs of the agendas of
individual Members of Congress which the National Taxpayers Union Foundation (NTUF)
establishes every Congress for each member.  By these standards, it is unprecedented.  Since
NTUF began recording this data, no member of Congress has ever had a spending agenda as large
as that proposed by NEA.  In other words, <em>the National Education Association's spending
agenda is more profligate than that of every single member of Congress since 1991</em>.
<br wp="br1"><br wp="br2">

<table border cellpadding=5 width="68%">
<tr>
