of resources for instruction, research, and library materials."</li>
  <ol>
    <li>Cost: $27 million</li>
    <li>Source:</li>
    <ol>
      <li>S 82, 103rd Congress, Establish higher education recruitment and retention
initiative.  Cost is $2 million.</li>
      <li>HR 3181, 102nd Congress, Amend Higher Education Act of 1965 to Improve
College and University Libraries.  According to the office of Representative
Kildee, the cost is $25 million.</li>
    </ol>
  </ol>
  <li>"Strengthening student financial assistance such as Pell Grants."</li>
  <ol>
    <li>Cost: $3,919 million</li>
    <li>Source:</li>
