<LI>
<A HREF="#I1">1 The Significance of Privatization and Choice for Education</A></LI>
<UL>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I2">The Modes of Privatization</A></LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I3">The Privatization Movement</A></LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I4">To Whom Is This Book Addressed</A></LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I5">Why Reforms Fail:  An Illustrative Scenario</A></LI>
