<A HREF="#I1">4 Lessons from OEO Fiasco</A></LI>
<UL>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I2">An Overview Of The OEO Project2 </A></LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I3">Implications of the OEO Project for Contracting Out</A></LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I4">Overcoming Union Opposition to Contracting Out</A></LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I5">The Role of School Management in Contracting Out</A></LI>
<LI>
<A HREF="#I6">The Allocation and Distribution of Instructional Time</A></LI>
